ps-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CurrencyService/Convert,2325.676837096255,3839.581818181818,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.CurrencyService/GetSupportedCurrencies,2864.123828486679,5826.311111111111,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-01,shippingservice,frontend-1,shippingservice-0,hipstershop.ShippingService/GetQuote,201.39352136459794,407.77777777777777,出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["cartservice-0", "cartservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "emailservice-1", "frontend-0", "frontend-1", "shippingservice-0"], "service_name": ["cartservice", "checkoutservice", "emailservice", "frontend", "redis", "shippingservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-01", "aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-06", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "status_combinations": "node_name,service_name,parent_pod,child_pod,operation_name,status_code,status_message,occurrence_count\naiops-k8s-04,frontend,frontend-2,frontend-2,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:1790\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,frontend-0,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:1609\naiops-k8s-07,frontend,frontend-1,frontend-1,hipstershop.AdService/GetAds,2,,出现次数:1468\n", "matched_anomaly": "A fault occurred from 2025-06-10T06:10:40Z to 2025-06-10T06:31:40Z. Please identify the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-10 06:10:40+00:00 to 2025-06-10 06:31:40+00:00"}, "log_analysis_findings": "根据采集到的日志数据，以下是分析结果：\n\n### 关键发现\n1. **错误模式**：\n   - `frontend` 服务频繁报错，内容为 `failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc =`，表明 `frontend` 无法从 `adservice` 获取广告数据。\n   - `adservice` 服务出现大量异常日志，包括 `java.lang.Error: Injected error` 和 `java.lang.Exception: Main : attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`，表明 `adservice` 存在注入错误和代理加载问题。\n\n2. **公共嫌疑人**：\n   - `adservice` 是多个 `frontend` 服务报错的共同目标，且其自身存在严重异常。\n\n3. **特殊故障模式**：\n   - 日志中未发现 `DNS` 或 `Port Misconfiguration` 相关的错误。\n\n### 分析结论\n根因可能是 `adservice` 服务因代理加载问题和注入错误导致无法正常响应 `frontend` 的请求。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"failed to get ads\", \"rpc error\", \"java.lang.Error\", \"Injected error\", \"java.lang.Exception\", \"Byteman agent\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice 因代理加载问题和注入错误（java.lang.Error: Injected error）导致无法响应 frontend 的请求。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-15363\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的调用链数据，我将对故障进行分析。从trace数据可以看出，系统在指定时间段内出现了显著的延迟异常。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"checkoutservice->cartservice\", \"frontend->checkoutservice\", \"frontend->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->redis\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice调用cartservice的GetCart操作从正常2.5ms激增至54.0s（延迟倍数21.6倍），frontend调用cartservice的GetCart操作从正常3.9ms激增至10.5s（延迟倍数2.7倍）\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice调用redis的HGET操作从正常1.7ms激增至53.3s（延迟倍数30.7倍），表明redis存在严重性能问题\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend调用checkoutservice的PlaceOrder操作从正常145-154ms激增至307-320s（延迟倍数约2.1倍），但主要是下游cartservice和redis延迟导致\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现分析**：\n\n1. **根因定位**：根据调用链拓扑，redis是cartservice的下游，cartservice是checkoutservice的下游。redis的HGET操作延迟激增30.7倍，导致cartservice性能严重下降，进而影响checkoutservice和frontend。\n\n2. **延迟模式**：\n   - redis → cartservice → checkoutservice → frontend 形成了明显的延迟传播路径\n   - 最下游的redis出现严重性能问题（53.3s vs 1.7ms）\n   - cartservice作为中间服务，受到redis影响，响应时间从毫秒级激增至秒级\n\n3. **错误传播**：虽然状态码显示都是\"2\"（成功），但延迟异常表明系统虽然能响应，但性能严重恶化，可能是资源瓶颈或网络问题导致。\n\n**建议**：需要进一步检查redis实例的资源使用情况、网络连接状况以及是否存在数据热点或锁竞争问题。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于采集到的指标数据，我对故障期间的异常情况进行了分析。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-03\",\n      \"reason\": \"节点内存使用率显著上升，从37.22%增加到45.06%，同时可用内存从10GB减少到8.69GB，表明存在内存资源瓶颈\",\n      \"evidence\": \"node_memory_usage_rate: 37.22% → 45.06% (变化率19.06%)，node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes: 10GB → 8.69GB (变化率14.07%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"paymentservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标出现显著异常，p99值从6.75秒飙升到47.14秒，变化率高达149.87%，表明服务响应时间严重恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99: 6753.73ms → 47137.6ms (变化率149.87%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"emailservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标异常，p99值从8.95秒增加到60.37秒，变化率148.36%，响应时间显著恶化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99: 8948.49ms → 60370.8ms (变化率148.36%)\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务响应时间异常，rrt_max p99值从387秒增加到528秒，表明用户请求处理延迟严重\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max p99: 387156.03ms → 528071.0ms (变化率30.79%)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 分析总结\n\n**主要发现：**\n1. **节点级问题**：`aiops-k8s-03`节点内存使用率显著上升，可能存在内存资源瓶颈\n2. **服务级问题**：多个关键服务（paymentservice、emailservice、frontend）的响应时间指标出现严重异常\n3. **影响范围**：故障影响了支付、邮件和前端等多个核心服务，用户体验受到严重影响\n\n**故障模式识别**：\n- 节点内存问题可能导致了服务性能下降的连锁反应\n- paymentservice和emailservice的响应时间异常最为显著，变化率接近150%\n- frontend作为用户入口，其响应时间恶化会直接影响整体用户体验\n\n建议进一步分析这些服务之间的调用关系和依赖，以确定根因的传播路径。"}
